						               													<description>Trivial Pursuit - Chocolate Edition is a very simple implementation of the traditional Trivial Pursuit game. The game proceeds in turns taken in clockwise order. On your turn, the player to your right will ask you the questions. The question cards in this case are actually chocolate bites in paper wrap (on which the questions are written). The player who knows the answer to both questions on one card / bite gets it (and presumably digests it, as well). If an answer was wrong, the card is returned into the box. The player with the most correct answers in the end of the game is the winner, and is awarded the golden prize (which is made of chocolate, of course).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
